                "invention-title": [
                    "Method and device for producing low-sulfur ship fuel by catalyzing heavy oil",
                    "催化重油生产低硫船燃的方法及装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method and a device for producing low-sulfur ship fuel by catalyzing heavy oil, and belongs to the technical field of petroleum refining. According to the technical scheme, heavy oil is subjected to catalytic hydrogenation and fractionation through a hydrogenation device to obtain a low-sulfur ship fuel blending component, and the low-sulfur ship fuel blending component is mixed with vacuum residue to obtain low-sulfur ship fuel; the device comprises a hydrogenation device, a hot high-pressure separation tank, a cold high-pressure separation tank, a cold low-pressure separation tank and a stripping tower, and the hydrogenation device comprises a filter, a raw material buffer tank, a heating furnace and a hydrogenation reactor. Under relatively mild reaction conditions and relatively low hydrogen consumption, the doping proportion of the heavy oil in the ship fuel can be greatly improved, indexes such as ship fuel density, viscosity, sulfur content, carbon residue and the like are ensured not to exceed the standard, the heating value of the ship fuel is greatly improved, the compatibility of the ship fuel is improved, and high-quality ship fuel products are ensured to be produced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种催化重油生产低硫船燃的方法及装置，属于石油炼制技术领域。其技术方案为：重油经加氢装置催化加氢和分馏得到低硫船燃调和组分，低硫船燃调和组分与减压渣油混合，得到低硫船燃；装置，包括加氢装置、热高分罐、冷高分罐、冷低分罐和汽提塔，加氢装置包括过滤器、原料缓冲罐、加热炉和加氢反应器。本发明在较缓和的反应条件和相对较低的氢耗下，可大幅提高重油在船燃中的掺入比例，保证了船燃密度、黏度、硫含量、残炭等指标不超标，大幅提高其发热值，提高船燃的相容性，保证生产优质的船燃产品。"
                }
            ]
